All those changes to ARAM and you _still_ don't make the one that actually matters : 

#Making the entire champion pool available to any participant of ARAM, thus negating "ARAM only accounts". 

######_Good job._{{sticker:zombie-brand-clap}}

The loss of {{item:3302}} on ARAM sounds like it will probably hurt certain champs like  {{champion:86}} {{champion:14}} or even the rarely seen but not unheard of full-tank/non-ap {{champion:75}} who actually have a need to farm minions for more than just gold income. 

Also I'm not going to be surprised if with the removal of {{item:3069}} that there will still be {{item:2053}} despite nothing for it to build into. 

**Edit:** Called it on  {{item:2053}}
